snippet.title: Happy 31st birthday, Amber Heard!
snippet.description:
This is a fan-made video dedicated to the amazing actress Amber Heard from the page Amber Heard Italia to wish happy birthday to her!

This video was made by Melania, Anna and Giorgia.
